"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-12-Paris-2024-Beyond-the-medals-friendship-respect-and-integrity-1w0nlN77rbi-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Copied  The Paris Olympic Games came to a celebratory close on Sunday, after two weeks of intense competitions, controversial calls and outcomes, and record-breaking feats. There were some touching moments during the games that showed people that the Olympics are not only about winning medals, but also about writing a story of friendship, respect and integrity among nations.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"